.claude/settings.local.json
.claude/scheduled_tasks.lock

# Internal working notes — kept local, not published
/idea.md
/start.md
/NOTES.md
/BUSINESS_PLAN.md
/BUILD_SERVICE_PLAN.md
/CAPABILITIES-ROADMAP.md
